      "seed": 1255598238,
      "version": 877,
      "versionNonce": 687150402,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775040093357,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "getShortUrl\n- fast, \n- unique, \n- short (5-7)\n1. random number generator not really good enough, high collision probability\n    - can read to check collision before new write\n2. hash the long url\n    - md5(longUrl) -> hash -> base64(hash)[0:6]\n3. counter\n    - increment a counter -> base64\n4. encrypted counter (if encryption key is leaked, counters are exposed)\n    - increment ounter → AES encrypt → base64 encode\n5. UUID7 generated",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "getShortUrl\n- fast, \n- unique, \n- short (5-7)\n1. random number generator not really good enough, high collision probability\n    - can read to check collision before new write\n2. hash the long url\n    - md5(longUrl) -> hash -> base64(hash)[0:6]\n3. counter\n    - increment a counter -> base64\n4. encrypted counter (if encryption key is leaked, counters are exposed)\n    - increment ounter → AES encrypt → base64 encode\n5. UUID7 generated",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
